Monkey 4028, a convicted felon and 4029's brother, turned out to have been an experienced escape artist. While serving time in an island prison, he hatched an escape plan along with two other monkey inmates which would involve fleeing the prison via the nearby bay to the mainland. After carefully observing the flow of the currents, he and the other inmates were able to construct a makeshift raft, two paddles, and dummy heads to fool the prison guards. Later that night, they escaped the prison under the cover of darkness, attempted to flee using the makeshift raft, and were never heard from again.
